            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/06/28/applevision-pro-purchase-notice/vr-mr-ar/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Ngan Ivan]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 05:58:51 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[VR 科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[影視娛樂]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[生活科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[買物情報]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Apple]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Apple Store]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Apple Vision Pro]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1246781</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">Apple Vision Pro 今日終於在香港正式開售，目前在各大 Apple Store 門市、官網或者安裝最新版本的 Apple Store App 均可以直接訂購 Apple Vision Pro，售價為 $27999 起。提供即日送貨和取貨服務，讓用戶能夠即時使用 Apple Vision Pro。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1246782" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/1-15-scaled-e1719551377989-694x378.jpg" alt="Apple Vision Pro" width="694" height="378" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/1-15-scaled-e1719551377989-694x378.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/1-15-scaled-e1719551377989-1280x697.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><figure id="attachment_1246784" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-1246784" style="width: 694px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="wp-image-1246784 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2-13-scaled-e1719551394537-694x380.jpg" alt="Apple Vision Pro" width="694" height="380" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2-13-scaled-e1719551394537-694x380.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2-13-scaled-e1719551394537-1280x701.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-1246784" class="wp-caption-text"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: 10pt;">▲ 目前網上預約示範服務最快可即日就預約到</span></figcaption></figure><p style="font-weight: 400;">希望直接前往門市購入 Apple Vision Pro 的用戶需要注意了，根據 Apple Store 官網顯示，目前 Apple Store 門市的 Apple Vision Pro 只限在網上成功預約產品示範的人士購買，而 Apple Store 官網和 Apple Store App 則可以直接購買。現場的 Apple Specialist 技術人員會與閣下進行 1 對 1 的示範，並會協助你進行面部掃描以及按視力等需要進行個人化設定（可即場直接量度所佩戴的眼鏡度數）。</p><figure id="attachment_1246790" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-1246790" style="width: 694px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="wp-image-1246790 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/3-8-scaled-e1719551749309-694x378.jpg" alt="Apple Vision Pro" width="694" height="378" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/3-8-scaled-e1719551749309-694x378.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/3-8-scaled-e1719551749309-1280x697.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-1246790" class="wp-caption-text"><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: #000000;">▲ Apple Store Online 上購買需要用到 iPhone 或 iPad</span></figcaption></figure><p>至於在 Apple Store 官網和 Apple Store App 上購買的用戶則需要使用到具備 FaceID 功能的 iPhone 或 iPad，掃描圖片後完成面部掃描。</p><figure id="attachment_1246791" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-1246791" style="width: 694px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="wp-image-1246791 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/4-5-scaled-e1719551768770-694x377.jpg" alt="Apple Vision Pro" width="694" height="377" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/4-5-scaled-e1719551768770-694x377.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/4-5-scaled-e1719551768770-1280x696.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-1246791" class="wp-caption-text"><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: #000000;">▲可選購 ZEISS Optical Inserts 鏡片</span></figcaption></figure><p>Apple Store 官網和 Apple Store App 上購買需要預先提供度數資訊，如有近視或老花的矯視需要， Apple 亦提供 ZEISS Optical Inserts 鏡片選購。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">資料及圖片來源：<a href="https://www.apple.com/hk/apple-vision-pro/">Apple </a></p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/14/apple-vision-pro-preorder-2/vr-mr-ar/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【教學】Apple Vision Pro 香港預訂教學　戴眼鏡也能輕鬆買 + 臉部掃描過程</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/28/iphone-23/mobile-phone/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">iPhone 將可用第三方熒幕及電池     True Tone 及電池健康指標都可支援</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/27/apple-says-no-retro-pc-emulators-on-the-app-store/fun-tech/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">App Store 禁 PC 模擬器上架，遊戲主機模擬器不受限制</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/28/applevision-pro-purchase-notice/vr-mr-ar/">Apple Vision Pro 香港開售，即日取貨送貨+購買須知</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
